{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">&quot;Re:|THM - Once upon a time&quot; is a rhythm game RPG that travels through reversed time. </h2>The rain rises from the bottom to the top, and defeated enemies come back to life. Meetings become separations, and the story heads towards the beginning. <br>Players will unravel the story of the separation of humans and monsters in reverse time. Experience the wonder of a world where time flows in reverse, something that cannot be experienced in reality.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154940/extras/Rain_CG_animation.gif?t=1675976358\" /><br>The hero Astelro, who defeated the Monster King, kills the human king,<br> Ankh. Using the reverse device called &quot;Ex&quot; that only the king has, he reverses the flow of time. <br>What Astelro couldn't bear to lose even by going back in time...<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154940/extras/4.png?t=1675976358\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Various wonders in reversed time</h2>The story progresses like a video being played in reverse. The story is unraveled by looking back on the hero Astelro's regrets.<br> Will he sometimes be tormented by his past actions?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154940/extras/\u30b7\u30fc\u30b1\u30f3\u30b9_01.gif?t=1675976358\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Real-time reverse rhythm game</h2>The biggest feature of this work is a rhythm game that can be reversed in real-time. Even if you make a mistake, you can immediately roll back and restart from that point.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154940/extras/steam_battle.gif?t=1675976358\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"TimeReverse!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2154940/a154d9af00bb03478c592c872c8f4b6